00:00:00.280 --> 00:00:05.480
Sahaja Yogini: … which is the point of evolution

00:00:05.720 --> 00:00:06.720
for all of us.

00:00:06.920 --> 00:00:11.720
And it gives great pleasure to Sahaja Yogis

00:00:11.920 --> 00:00:14.240
to see so many other people

00:00:14.440 --> 00:00:16.320
coming along to get their realization.

00:00:16.560 --> 00:00:22.520
Because the experience, once you achieve it,

00:00:22.720 --> 00:00:26.600
makes you collectively conscious and puts you in touch,

00:00:26.800 --> 00:00:31.240
in a very real way, with the vibrations of other people

00:00:31.440 --> 00:00:33.920
and with your own vibrations, of course

00:00:34.160 --> 00:00:39.120
so that you're able to feel the exact condition of your subtle body,

00:00:39.320 --> 00:00:43.840
and your spirit, and your chakras, which are these.

00:00:44.080 --> 00:00:48.360
these coloured circles here represent

00:00:48.560 --> 00:00:52.680
the subtle transformers of energy that are placed within us

00:00:52.880 --> 00:00:56.720
along the sympathetic nervous system.

00:00:56.920 --> 00:01:02.800
And in the centre there,

00:01:03.200 --> 00:01:07.240
between the yellow and blue lines,

00:01:07.440 --> 00:01:11.520
is the area in which the Kundalini energy rises

00:01:11.720 --> 00:01:15.480
when it's awakened by the presence of another being

00:01:15.680 --> 00:01:19.080
who already has that awakened within him

00:01:19.280 --> 00:01:21.440
and is emitting the vibrations

00:01:21.640 --> 00:01:27.520
that are the same as the universal Kundalini energy.

00:01:29.520 --> 00:01:34.760
Kundalini in Christian terms is called the Holy Spirit,

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:37.760
and it's the same energy that's described

00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:41.760
in the New Testament as the “cool wind”.

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:46.680
In Indian scriptures it's described as the Chaitanya,

00:01:46.880 --> 00:01:52.280
as cool vibrations, and in Muslim scriptures it is called the Ruh,

00:01:52.480 --> 00:01:55.680
and also described as cool vibrations.

00:01:55.880 --> 00:01:58.720
And these cool vibrations that you feel once

00:01:58.920 --> 00:02:02.560
you receive the awakening

00:02:02.760 --> 00:02:08.640
are the vibrations of absolute truth.

00:02:10.320 --> 00:02:13.720
Once you develop this awareness,

00:02:13.920 --> 00:02:17.000
you're able to ask any absolute question,

00:02:17.200 --> 00:02:21.760
and, by holding your hands out, you can ask

00:02:22.000 --> 00:02:25.520
if you're an atheist, you can ask the existence of God.

00:02:25.760 --> 00:02:31.000
And whether you get a cool or a warm vibration,

00:02:31.200 --> 00:02:37.080
you can tell whether what you're asking about is true or not true.

00:02:37.280 --> 00:02:40.320
So there's no need to use the intellect anymore

00:02:40.560 --> 00:02:41.920
to try and work out things,

00:02:42.160 --> 00:02:45.880
because that's a limited sphere of activity;

00:02:46.120 --> 00:02:49.560
but you actually, once you get your realization,

00:02:49.760 --> 00:02:53.760
you go beyond mere thinking

00:02:54.000 --> 00:02:59.840
into the unlimited, into the divine area.

00:03:00.880 --> 00:03:04.840
I think …

00:03:05.880 --> 00:03:10.440
it's a relief to be with people who are seeking their spirit,

00:03:10.640 --> 00:03:14.560
who do have a desire to know the Divine

00:03:14.760 --> 00:03:20.000
and to understand those …

00:03:20.800 --> 00:03:26.000
things that in this society have almost become taboo subjects,

00:03:26.200 --> 00:03:31.640
that there's so much emphasis around us, in our upbringing,

00:03:31.840 --> 00:03:37.680
on material success, and competition, and …

00:03:38.320 --> 00:03:41.880
doing better than everybody else in achieving things,

00:03:42.120 --> 00:03:46.160
that the subtle things, that are much more important,

00:03:46.360 --> 00:03:49.040
get pushed completely into the background.

00:03:49.240 --> 00:03:53.760
And sometimes we feel as if we are quite out of step with

00:03:54.000 --> 00:03:57.560
everything, because we know that this is uneasy feeling

00:03:57.760 --> 00:04:01.240
that there's something wrong with the world at the moment

00:04:01.440 --> 00:04:04.160
but we can't put it right ourselves,

00:04:04.360 --> 00:04:08.240
and it can be quite distressing.

00:04:09.040 --> 00:04:13.480
In my experience, once I actually

00:04:13.680 --> 00:04:17.760
received my realization from Mother, two years ago in Melbourne

00:04:18.000 --> 00:04:20.760
at a programme like this,

00:04:21.000 --> 00:04:24.440
I couldn't believe it that it had actually …

00:04:24.720 --> 00:04:26.400
that I had found what I was looking for,

00:04:26.600 --> 00:04:30.680
without even quite knowing what it was that I was looking for.

00:04:30.880 --> 00:04:33.920
And …it's because

00:04:34.160 --> 00:04:36.720
at first you try and understand you with your intellect,

00:04:36.920 --> 00:04:40.320
and it doesn't seem to even make sense that …

00:04:40.560 --> 00:04:43.080
and a lot of people, actually,

00:04:43.280 --> 00:04:45.840
their self-esteem has been so damaged by their seeking,

00:04:46.080 --> 00:04:52.000
that it's hard to believe that you yourself could have

00:04:52.800 --> 00:04:58.640
this quality within you, just waiting to be awakened.

00:05:00.720 --> 00:05:04.440
So, perhaps, before Mataji arrives,

00:05:04.640 --> 00:05:10.240
it would be good if you could just sit quietly and …

00:05:12.320 --> 00:05:14.200
don't try and do anything.

00:05:14.400 --> 00:05:16.760
If you've been in the habit of doing

00:05:17.000 --> 00:05:20.280
particular types of meditation or techniques,

00:05:20.520 --> 00:05:24.600
just try and put them aside and just have a completely open mind

00:05:24.800 --> 00:05:27.240
about this experience because it is different,

00:05:27.440 --> 00:05:29.680
although the terms may be familiar to you

00:05:29.880 --> 00:05:34.840
from readings and teachings that you've had.

00:05:35.080 --> 00:05:38.400
It's best to sort of try and approach it like a child,

00:05:38.720 --> 00:05:41.120
with complete openness and freshness.

00:05:41.360 --> 00:05:45.000
There's nothing frightening about the experience,

00:05:45.200 --> 00:05:47.240
because it is, in fact,

00:05:47.440 --> 00:05:51.920
a gift of God to us.

00:05:52.280 --> 00:05:55.320
And God is Compassion and Love.

00:05:55.520 --> 00:05:59.600
And the vibrations that you feel once your Kundalini is awakened

00:05:59.800 --> 00:06:03.760
are those vibrations that come from that Being.

00:06:04.000 --> 00:06:07.720
And there is nothing to be afraid of, although some books do say

00:06:07.920 --> 00:06:12.840
that Kundalini awakening can be dangerous and so on.

00:06:13.680 --> 00:06:15.560
The people who've written those have experienced

00:06:15.760 --> 00:06:18.680
something quite different.

00:06:18.880 --> 00:06:24.000
But the actual experience should give you peace and joy,

00:06:24.200 --> 00:06:26.080
which is absolute.

00:06:26.280 --> 00:06:30.920
So, if you can just try and just be at peace now,

00:06:31.160 --> 00:06:34.120
and quiet, and in your receptive frame of mind,

00:06:34.320 --> 00:06:39.400
and enjoy the experience when Mother comes.

00:06:39.640 --> 00:06:42.720
Thank you.

00:06:59.000 --> 00:07:00.880
Sahaja Yogi: Again, ladies and gentlemen,

00:07:01.120 --> 00:07:04.920
it gives me a great pleasure, especially to the …

00:07:09.640 --> 00:07:12.640
Shri Mataji: Thank you very much.

00:07:20.120 --> 00:07:23.000
SY: … especially to the people who have come for the first time.

00:07:23.200 --> 00:07:24.760
There are many who couldn't come

00:07:25.000 --> 00:07:27.800
either last evening or today to the workshop.

00:07:28.040 --> 00:07:30.720
To all of you, welcome.

00:07:30.920 --> 00:07:34.800
Shri Mataji is here, for the first time in Perth, to

00:07:35.040 --> 00:07:37.560
to grant Self-realization,

00:07:37.760 --> 00:07:41.680
not just on a one-to-one basis but to as many people

00:07:41.880 --> 00:07:44.720
as desired from their heart.

00:07:44.920 --> 00:07:46.720
Many got it last night.

00:07:46.920 --> 00:07:52.400
Some came to the workshop today and experienced something more.

00:07:52.680 --> 00:07:55.240
All of you have to get it because this is the time

00:07:55.440 --> 00:07:59.560
when the grace of God is overflowing, and …

00:07:59.840 --> 00:08:05.480
all of the true seekers of ages have to get their Self-realization.

00:08:05.800 --> 00:08:09.000
It's the reward of their seeking, it's the blessing

00:08:09.200 --> 00:08:12.280
of their past births

00:08:12.480 --> 00:08:16.280
and all the seeking of God over the ages.

00:08:17.000 --> 00:08:19.800
We've all probably been a Christian, we've all been a Jew,

00:08:20.040 --> 00:08:21.800
we've all been a Muslim.

00:08:22.040 --> 00:08:24.440
We've been worshippers

00:08:24.680 --> 00:08:29.080
of God the Father and God the Mother

00:08:29.280 --> 00:08:32.040
at many many times in history.

00:08:32.240 --> 00:08:35.480
And so, now the time has come when we can get

00:08:35.680 --> 00:08:38.320
that final step in our evolution,

00:08:38.520 --> 00:08:44.120
which is just to be triggered by an enlightened being

00:08:44.320 --> 00:08:47.760
and which, once you get it,

00:08:48.000 --> 00:08:50.280
you can develop to that point

00:08:50.480 --> 00:08:53.360
where you become totally one with God.

00:08:53.600 --> 00:08:55.160
This is the real yoga.

00:08:55.360 --> 00:08:59.120
Yoga, as you know, means union, oneness with God.

00:08:59.320 --> 00:09:03.440
It's not exercises, it's not some discipline.

00:09:03.680 --> 00:09:08.080
It's the actualization of Self-realization.

00:09:08.280 --> 00:09:11.840
And so, without any further introduction by me,

00:09:12.080 --> 00:09:14.840
it gives me again great pleasure, ladies and gentlemen,

00:09:15.080 --> 00:09:20.920
to introduce to you Her Holiness Shri Mataji Nirmala Devi.

00:09:42.760 --> 00:09:48.680
Shri Mataji: To all the seekers of truth and joy I bow.

00:09:52.560 --> 00:09:55.400
It was really nice this morning

00:09:55.600 --> 00:09:59.000
to meet some earnest seekers come down

00:09:59.200 --> 00:10:02.000
to the place where I live

00:10:02.200 --> 00:10:07.360
and to get their ultimate what they are seeking.

00:10:08.680 --> 00:10:14.600
We have to know that God has created us with a purpose.

00:10:15.280 --> 00:10:19.800
He has worked for so many years,

00:10:20.440 --> 00:10:25.920
He has made us human beings with such care and love.

00:10:26.160 --> 00:10:29.120
There has to be a purpose behind it.

00:10:29.320 --> 00:10:33.160
We also know that we have not yet found our purpose,

00:10:33.360 --> 00:10:36.840
and that's why we are seeking.

00:10:37.840 --> 00:10:40.600
If we understand that,

00:10:40.800 --> 00:10:46.120
then one must know that something has to happen.

00:10:46.320 --> 00:10:48.840
God has to save His creation.

00:10:49.080 --> 00:10:54.040
And His greatest creation is a human being.

00:10:54.240 --> 00:10:56.680
This is what He has done out of all the creation —

00:10:56.880 --> 00:11:00.720
that you tried to evolve,

00:11:00.920 --> 00:11:05.080
and that's how human beings are created.

00:11:05.400 --> 00:11:09.000
Only thing was, a human being was given a freedom

00:11:09.200 --> 00:11:13.600
to choose between the right and the wrong for life.

00:11:13.840 --> 00:11:18.920
It so happened that human being, in their error, naiveness —

00:11:19.160 --> 00:11:21.800
I should say, in ignorance ,

00:11:22.040 --> 00:11:24.760
did lots of mistakes. Doesn't matter.

00:11:25.000 --> 00:11:26.880
Even if they have done,

00:11:27.120 --> 00:11:31.320
most of them have come to right conclusion;

00:11:31.520 --> 00:11:33.000
and that right conclusion,

00:11:33.200 --> 00:11:36.200
as I told you yesterday, sums up like this:

00:11:36.400 --> 00:11:41.440
that whatever is going to happen to us further than this,

00:11:41.760 --> 00:11:46.000
it has to be spontaneous, is a living process

00:11:46.200 --> 00:11:48.760
that has made us human being, nothing dead.

00:11:49.000 --> 00:11:51.920
If the living process has to work it out,

00:11:52.160 --> 00:11:54.400
then it has to be spontaneous.

00:11:54.600 --> 00:11:56.520
We cannot work it out.

00:11:56.720 --> 00:12:02.600
Secondly, that you cannot pay for it, or you cannot manoeuvre it.

00:12:03.120 --> 00:12:06.720
And thirdly, that you cannot put in any effort,

00:12:06.920 --> 00:12:08.480
it has to be effortless.

00:12:08.680 --> 00:12:13.240
If it is the most vital thing for God, it has to be effortless.

00:12:13.440 --> 00:12:17.440
So that's how we reach certain conclusions:

00:12:17.640 --> 00:12:23.080
that Self-realization, if it is the epitome of our evolution,

00:12:23.280 --> 00:12:28.400
it has to be absolutely freely given

00:12:28.640 --> 00:12:33.640
and has to happen in a very spontaneous way.

00:12:33.880 --> 00:12:36.280
Yesterday I explained to you in short

00:12:36.480 --> 00:12:41.160
all the various types of ideas people have about Self-realization,

00:12:41.360 --> 00:12:46.640
and what we have to expect about Self-realization.

00:12:47.120 --> 00:12:50.760
We had another enquiry this morning about Kundalini,

00:12:51.000 --> 00:12:54.240
that a gentleman asked Me a question saying

00:12:54.440 --> 00:12:59.760
that he has read some books which are all the time warning

00:13:00.000 --> 00:13:02.160
that Kundalini business is very difficult,

00:13:02.360 --> 00:13:05.200
it comes up to a point but not

00:13:05.400 --> 00:13:08.760
beyond a point, and all sorts of stories.

00:13:09.000 --> 00:13:14.160
And I have to tell you that that's not true.

00:13:14.360 --> 00:13:17.120
Kundalini is your own mother.

00:13:17.320 --> 00:13:19.920
You have your individual mother.

00:13:20.160 --> 00:13:23.720
And she is waiting all the time, all these years,

00:13:23.920 --> 00:13:26.800
just to give you your second birth.

00:13:27.040 --> 00:13:30.080
She never harms you, she never troubles you,

00:13:30.280 --> 00:13:32.560
she doesn't do anything of that kind.

00:13:32.760 --> 00:13:37.720
It's … I don't know, the people who do not know how to do the thing

00:13:37.920 --> 00:13:42.160
or who have no authority must be doing all these kinds of tricks

00:13:42.360 --> 00:13:47.000
and must be suffering from Kundalini awakening.

00:13:47.200 --> 00:13:49.760
I know of one gentleman

00:13:50.000 --> 00:13:54.680
who, in Kashmir, said that he's got Kundalini awakening

00:13:54.880 --> 00:13:57.760
and he had tremendous heat and tremendous burning

00:13:58.000 --> 00:14:01.920
and all sorts of things, and that …

00:14:02.800 --> 00:14:05.760
he … “it's a very dangerous thing”, he has written a book on that,

00:14:06.000 --> 00:14:09.880
some sort of a … I'm forgetting the name of the book.

00:14:10.120 --> 00:14:14.360
Now, this gentleman himself is leading a very horrible life.

00:14:14.560 --> 00:14:17.680
Of that I've been able to find out.

00:14:17.880 --> 00:14:20.920
He has all sorts of relations, and he's leading

00:14:21.160 --> 00:14:25.080
a very ridiculous life, not suitable for any saint.

00:14:25.280 --> 00:14:28.840
If such a man has to have a Kundalini awakening …

00:14:29.080 --> 00:14:31.760
I can't understand how can Kundalini come to him,

00:14:32.000 --> 00:14:36.600
but must be some sort of a God's anger on him

00:14:36.800 --> 00:14:41.080
that he has felt this kind of a feeling within him, maybe,

00:14:41.280 --> 00:14:44.880
or maybe he has been to somebody who is a wrong type of a person,

00:14:45.120 --> 00:14:50.480
who has awakened the Kundalini

00:14:50.680 --> 00:14:53.120
without any authority.

00:14:53.320 --> 00:14:56.520
And maybe, that time, the first deity, as I told you

00:14:56.720 --> 00:14:58.840
is it there? the chart is not there?

00:14:59.080 --> 00:15:02.040
the first deity I told you

00:15:02.240 --> 00:15:08.080
did not like it and got angry.

00:15:08.280 --> 00:15:11.240
And the whole sympathetic nervous system on the left-hand side

00:15:11.440 --> 00:15:14.440
and right-hand side got angry.

00:15:14.640 --> 00:15:18.400
And when that happen, the person can develop lot of heat

00:15:18.640 --> 00:15:21.600
and lot of blisters.

00:15:21.800 --> 00:15:24.240
I have seen a person getting a blister all over,

00:15:24.440 --> 00:15:27.360
all round his neck.

00:15:27.560 --> 00:15:29.440
At the very outset I must tell you

00:15:29.680 --> 00:15:35.560
that heat is the sign of

00:15:37.560 --> 00:15:41.440
violent action.

00:15:41.680 --> 00:15:44.760
Say, for example, if you heat the helium gas,

00:15:45.000 --> 00:15:49.760
the molecules of the helium gas start going all round.

00:15:50.000 --> 00:15:53.920
They are very volatile, they start moving in a way

00:15:54.160 --> 00:15:59.040
that you feel that two armies are fighting.

00:15:59.240 --> 00:16:01.400
Then you find that ten armies are fighting,

00:16:01.600 --> 00:16:04.000
then you find all of them are fighting with each other.

00:16:04.200 --> 00:16:07.760
But if you cool it down, their action is very collective;

00:16:08.000 --> 00:16:11.640
they move in a smooth manner, in a very collective manner.

00:16:11.840 --> 00:16:16.040
So, one can see that when we are heated up also ,

00:16:16.240 --> 00:16:18.360
you see, a man is very hot-tempered

00:16:18.680 --> 00:16:24.760
means he is a very … angry person,

00:16:25.000 --> 00:16:27.680
and he cannot carry on with others, he has no patience.

00:16:27.880 --> 00:16:32.320
But when we see that a person is cool, is collected,

00:16:32.520 --> 00:16:34.560
then we say he is a nice person.

00:16:34.760 --> 00:16:39.760
In the same way, if you feel heat from your Kundalini,

00:16:40.000 --> 00:16:43.120
then be sure that something is wrong that is resisting you.

00:16:43.320 --> 00:16:45.760
Even while giving realization in the beginning,

00:16:46.000 --> 00:16:49.600
you do feel little heat because the heat of the body has to go out.

00:16:49.800 --> 00:16:53.280
But today I'm going to tell you more about,

00:16:53.480 --> 00:16:56.280
particularly more about the chakras

00:16:56.480 --> 00:17:00.320
and not about the general things that I told you last time.

00:17:00.520 --> 00:17:02.320
In any case, you can get the book,

00:17:02.520 --> 00:17:06.280
and you can come to our centres and clarify it more and more.

00:17:06.480 --> 00:17:09.320
But, as much as possible, today I will try

00:17:09.520 --> 00:17:11.320
to tell you about the chakras,

00:17:11.560 --> 00:17:15.760
how we spoil them,

00:17:16.000 --> 00:17:18.760
and what are the effects of these subtle chakras,

00:17:19.000 --> 00:17:24.840
which look after our gross plexuses within our body.

00:17:30.080 --> 00:17:32.120
Please be seated.

00:17:32.400 --> 00:17:35.080
Now, the first chakra, as I told you,

00:17:35.280 --> 00:17:37.240
is called as the Mooladhara Chakra.

00:17:37.480 --> 00:17:40.480
I'm sorry.

00:17:40.800 --> 00:17:42.680
(Aside) Is it all right now? Can you see it?

00:17:42.880 --> 00:17:45.120
Sahaja Yogi: Just raise it slightly [unclear].

00:17:45.320 --> 00:17:48.440
Shri Mataji: You can't hear? All right.

00:17:48.680 --> 00:17:52.680
Now, this is the first centre, which is a subtle centre within us.

00:17:52.880 --> 00:17:57.640
Now, this centre is manifesting outside

00:17:57.840 --> 00:18:01.080
what you call the pelvic plexus.

00:18:01.280 --> 00:18:06.520
The pelvic plexus is responsible for all our excretions.

00:18:06.760 --> 00:18:10.920
Whether you like it or not, it is there, it is present within us,

00:18:11.160 --> 00:18:17.040
and it looks after all our excretory …

00:18:18.160 --> 00:18:20.880
functions.

00:18:21.640 --> 00:18:26.600
It is important to see

00:18:26.800 --> 00:18:30.400
that this chakra is placed under the Kundalini.

00:18:30.720 --> 00:18:32.760
So, when the Kundalini rises …

00:18:33.000 --> 00:18:36.600
the Kundalini is the power within you,

00:18:36.800 --> 00:18:42.440
the pure power of desire,

00:18:42.680 --> 00:18:47.200
the desire that you want to become one with the Divine.

00:18:47.400 --> 00:18:50.600
Now, it lies below,

00:18:50.800 --> 00:18:54.520
this chakra lies below, is a very important point —

00:18:54.720 --> 00:19:00.280
that this chakra does not play any part

00:19:00.520 --> 00:19:02.720
in the ascent of the Kundalini,

00:19:02.920 --> 00:19:06.480
because Kundalini doesn't pierce through it.

00:19:06.720 --> 00:19:10.160
On the contrary, if this chakra is pure,

00:19:10.360 --> 00:19:15.360
the information about somebody who can raise your Kundalini

00:19:15.600 --> 00:19:18.760
can be easily communicated through this chakra.

00:19:19.000 --> 00:19:23.200
But it does not

00:19:23.440 --> 00:19:26.600
play any part in our evolution.

