Sahaja Yogi: Are you saying that She emits emanation, that …

01:17:06.760 --> 01:17:10.920
Seeker: No. No, [unclear], [this was the problem].

01:17:11.160 --> 01:17:12.920
And …

01:17:13.160 --> 01:17:16.200
Shri Mataji: I can't hear her.

01:17:16.400 --> 01:17:19.480
Madam, please get up. We can't hear you. All right?

01:17:19.680 --> 01:17:21.720
Seeker: I can understand about the enlightenment,

01:17:21.920 --> 01:17:24.240
but I can't understand about the emanations

01:17:24.440 --> 01:17:29.080
that You [unclear] [impossible]

01:17:29.280 --> 01:17:31.720
[unclear]

01:17:31.920 --> 01:17:32.720
Shri Mataji: What is she ,

01:17:32.920 --> 01:17:34.440
Sahaja Yogi: She can understand about the enlightenment.

01:17:34.760 --> 01:17:37.480
She cannot understand about the emanations of,

01:17:37.680 --> 01:17:39.840
probably she means Your power.

01:17:40.080 --> 01:17:42.680
Shri Mataji: You will understand that, all right? Gradually.

01:17:42.880 --> 01:17:45.840
Everything you can't understand in one day, can you?

01:17:46.080 --> 01:17:48.400
You will understand everything. You don't worry about Me.

01:17:48.720 --> 01:17:50.200
You just worry about yourself.

01:17:50.400 --> 01:17:53.000
I've not said anything about Myself, have I said?

01:17:53.200 --> 01:17:55.120
I never said anything.

01:17:55.320 --> 01:17:59.680
I've been very humble. I've never said anything. I dare not.

01:17:59.880 --> 01:18:03.800
Because it's not wise, I've learnt it.

01:18:04.040 --> 01:18:06.040
See, those who said it had a bad time.

01:18:06.240 --> 01:18:08.160
It's difficult. If you say something about yourself,

01:18:08.360 --> 01:18:11.240
suddenly the ego will come and just punch at you.

01:18:11.440 --> 01:18:14.760
No, it's very bad. I've never said a word about Myself.

01:18:15.000 --> 01:18:16.600
So you don't try to understand Me just now,

01:18:16.800 --> 01:18:18.360
first you understand yourself, all right?

01:18:18.560 --> 01:18:21.760
Then you understand Me.

01:18:23.000 --> 01:18:23.800
Sahaja Yogi: Any other questions?

01:18:24.040 --> 01:18:27.080
Otherwise we'll have the experience of Self-realization.

01:18:27.280 --> 01:18:28.920
This is what Mother has come for.

01:18:29.160 --> 01:18:31.760
Really a lecture is not the important part,

01:18:32.000 --> 01:18:34.400
the experience of Self-realization is it.

01:18:34.600 --> 01:18:38.440
We'll switch the fans off, and you'll feel it for yourself.

01:18:38.640 --> 01:18:41.720
Any other questions?

01:18:41.920 --> 01:18:43.720
Could you turn the fans off?

01:18:43.920 --> 01:18:47.400
Seeker: If we're Your devotees, do you also look after us?

01:18:47.720 --> 01:18:53.120
SY: If these people are Your devotees, do You look after them?

01:18:53.320 --> 01:18:56.280
Shri Mataji: What else I,I look after them.

01:18:56.480 --> 01:19:02.000
Ask them, better ask them if I've looked after them or not.

01:19:03.760 --> 01:19:05.240
Sahaja Yogi: I think it's obvious that

01:19:05.440 --> 01:19:08.040
insofar as all of us have got physically well;

01:19:08.240 --> 01:19:13.440
our nervous, mental, psychological problems have been healed;

01:19:13.680 --> 01:19:16.680
if we're endangered by an accident,

01:19:16.880 --> 01:19:21.360
if there's any particular problem which we want to solve,

01:19:21.680 --> 01:19:24.120
within our own life or within relationships,

01:19:24.320 --> 01:19:28.920
we put that at the attention of Almighty God,

01:19:29.920 --> 01:19:33.040
and by doing so we find that it gets solved.

01:19:33.240 --> 01:19:37.760
We've got all sorts of little methods

01:19:38.000 --> 01:19:40.720
by which we work things out.

01:19:40.920 --> 01:19:42.640
We showed you some of them today,

01:19:42.840 --> 01:19:44.760
in working out how the chakras are cleared.

01:19:45.000 --> 01:19:47.720
You can learn all of these things at the centre.

01:19:47.920 --> 01:19:52.720
There are certain aspects which you won't fully understand

01:19:52.920 --> 01:19:56.640
until you actually achieve the awakening of Kundalini,

01:19:56.840 --> 01:19:59.000
but as you grow in it, you'll understand more fully

01:19:59.200 --> 01:20:00.720
how the blessings of God

01:20:00.920 --> 01:20:03.760
actually descend upon you in a tremendous way.

01:20:04.000 --> 01:20:07.760
You get, your well-being is cared for, your health is cared for.

01:20:08.000 --> 01:20:11.120
Your psychological problems are solved.

01:20:11.320 --> 01:20:13.400
You become a complete and whole person,

01:20:13.600 --> 01:20:15.400
and this is the very beautiful part.

01:20:15.600 --> 01:20:18.360
When this lady asked is enlightenment synonymous

01:20:18.600 --> 01:20:20.520
with Self-realization,

01:20:20.720 --> 01:20:24.000
the answer is yes, but it's a growth process.

01:20:24.200 --> 01:20:27.760
You touch it or maybe you go more than that at the beginning

01:20:28.000 --> 01:20:31.040
and from that touching of Self-realization

01:20:31.240 --> 01:20:34.800
you grow from that point to a complete realized being.

01:20:35.040 --> 01:20:37.360
But you are an enlightened being because you've started

01:20:37.600 --> 01:20:40.760
that final journey in your spiritual evolution.

01:20:41.000 --> 01:20:42.880
We've had a human evolution this far.

01:20:43.120 --> 01:20:45.320
Now we've reached our spiritual evolution,

01:20:45.520 --> 01:20:48.120
and the road is very very rapid now.

01:20:48.320 --> 01:20:50.760
Because in this lifetime we can achieve

01:20:51.000 --> 01:20:53.120
that state of full realization,

01:20:53.320 --> 01:20:56.120
just by these techniques, very simple techniques

01:20:56.320 --> 01:21:00.600
that will be shown to you by the devotees of Shri Mataji.

01:21:00.840 --> 01:21:04.480
Shri Mataji: But I must confess one thing to you people:

01:21:04.800 --> 01:21:07.600
that your guru was very allergic to flowers and things,

01:21:07.800 --> 01:21:10.760
I'm very allergic to this dress, absolutely.

01:21:11.000 --> 01:21:12.720
Because this is not your style.

01:21:12.920 --> 01:21:14.720
You see, this dress is to be worn by people

01:21:14.920 --> 01:21:17.640
who lead an absolute celibate life

01:21:17.840 --> 01:21:21.080
and is meant for people who are not householders.

01:21:21.280 --> 01:21:24.240
And another thing is, if you read Valmiki Ramayana

01:21:24.440 --> 01:21:27.200
I don't know people read that or not, where Shri Sita

01:21:27.400 --> 01:21:31.080
has said that a sannyasi has nothing to do with householders at all.

01:21:31.280 --> 01:21:37.120
If there's a real sannyasi, he should stay out of the city,

01:21:37.320 --> 01:21:39.840
out of the village, only for one day.

01:21:40.080 --> 01:21:43.240
And he is to be given one-day alms and finished with it.

01:21:43.440 --> 01:21:45.400
Because you know what happened with Her,

01:21:45.600 --> 01:21:47.120
that Ravana came in this dress,

01:21:47.320 --> 01:21:49.320
and that's how I'm very allergic to this dress.

01:21:49.520 --> 01:21:52.200
Because it's not true, it's not true.

01:21:52.400 --> 01:21:54.760
Have you renounced the whole world? You have not.

01:21:55.000 --> 01:21:57.320
So, not to go in for this kind of a thing,

01:21:57.640 --> 01:22:01.440
you have to be normal people, you have to be living normally,

01:22:01.640 --> 01:22:03.000
accepting what you are

01:22:03.200 --> 01:22:05.360
and not announcing something which you are not.

01:22:05.560 --> 01:22:06.800
You see, this is what the gurus do

01:22:07.040 --> 01:22:08.640
they give you a dress and these things.

01:22:08.840 --> 01:22:10.440
So, if you want to have Sahaja Yoga

01:22:10.760 --> 01:22:13.080
of course, today I hope I'll give you realization,

01:22:13.280 --> 01:22:14.920
but afterwards you give up all this nonsense,

01:22:15.200 --> 01:22:16.160
you become normal people.

01:22:16.360 --> 01:22:18.000
You have to be absolutely normal.

01:22:18.200 --> 01:22:21.440
Nothing abnormal about it, recluses, funny type not.

01:22:21.640 --> 01:22:24.080
We have to get the whole world out of [their ?] problems.

01:22:24.280 --> 01:22:27.480
We can't just do it for ourself, individual some sort of a nonsense.

01:22:27.720 --> 01:22:31.040
No, we have to be responsible for the whole world,

01:22:31.240 --> 01:22:33.120
and we have to be absolutely normal people,

01:22:33.320 --> 01:22:37.240
behave in a normal way, not in an abnormal way, all right?

01:22:37.440 --> 01:22:39.480
So I'm very allergic to this dress.

01:22:39.680 --> 01:22:41.920
I'm just telling you, I hope I give you realization,

01:22:42.160 --> 01:22:45.200
because you are seekers, I can see that, all of you are seekers.

01:22:45.400 --> 01:22:46.760
You should get your realization.

01:22:47.000 --> 01:22:48.560
But I'm absolutely allergic to this.

01:22:48.760 --> 01:22:50.360
Because their guru is allergic to flowers.

01:22:50.560 --> 01:22:53.640
Imagine, God is so fond of flowers. I can't do without flowers.

01:22:53.840 --> 01:22:59.720
I can't understand how can any saintly man be allergic to flowers.

01:23:02.800 --> 01:23:03.480
So …

01:23:03.680 --> 01:23:07.680
Sahaja Yogi: OK. Then, any last question? Then we'll have it.

01:23:09.200 --> 01:23:12.200
OK.
